##FHO Uniararas Github Badge

This code is dumb and way too f***ing long.
You can improve this by...
- Changing the base64 code on [`logo`](https://b64.io) to a [better image](https://b64.io).
- Changing the `style`. You can choose from `plastic`,`flat`,`flat-square`, `for-the-badge` and `social`.
- Changing the message color at `-Uniararas-[here]?` and the `labelColor`.
- And changing the `logoWidth`.
